<Title>Fun and Functional, but...
<Date>Fri Jan 05 00:00:00 CST 2007
<Content>I really like the features and interface. I wasn't happy about the number of new software programs put on my computer and I didn't know what they were until it was finished.   However, I had it less than 24 hours when the joystick broke. Honestly, it seems almost too light and flimsy to last very long. My camera has a joystick about the same size that is much more robust and has worked for almost 2 years. I'm getting the MP3 player replaced, but... that doesn't help when the joystick is still apparently quite flimsy.  
<Overall>4

