<Content>Tons of features even if you don't listen to music.  The music is crisp, clear and can get loud.  The video screen has unbeatable resolution.  You can subscribe to any music service.  Works excellent with Window Media player, the Creative software will be needed for more detailed editing of play lists.  For less than 140 (2 gig) model I don't see this being beat.  
